	<dl>
	<dt>I would love to vote but will be out...</dt>
	<dd><p>I would love to vote but will be out of the country on the day and unfortunately my postal vote won't arrive before I go away.</p> <p>Surely there's got to be a better way?</p> <p>Crap or what?</p>
	<small>
	written 7th Apr 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/190">Email this
